HEADWORD: Pebrine
<hw>Pe`brine"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<def>An epidemic disease of the silkworm, characterized by the presence
of minute vibratory corpuscles in the blood.</def>⟦br⟧
